Direct Known Subclasses:
LoginPanel, RemAttributeList
public class AttributeList
extends javax.swing.JPanel
implements ContextHelp

Attribute list to layout components upon a panel line by line with a label at the beginning of each line. May be used e.g. to edit fields of a single database table record.
